<img src="https://github.com/akatuituji/Pic_blog/blob/master/20200922224203.png" alt="avatar" loading="lazy"></p>
<h2 id="2-malaria_deaths_age">2. malaria_deaths_age：</h2>
<p><img src="https://github.com/akatuituji/Pic_blog/blob/master/20200922233943.png" alt="avatar" loading="lazy"><br>
x-axis: Year/age group, y-axis: Deaths. Because there are 30780 rows, we will not set entity as x-axis. Instead we choose age and year to visualize and use seabon package. There are two graphs, one is for Year and the other is for age.<br>
<img src="https://github.com/akatuituji/Pic_blog/blob/master/20200922233407.png" alt="avatar" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://github.com/akatuituji/Pic_blog/blob/master/20200922233417.png" alt="avatar" loading="lazy"></p>
<h2 id="3-malaria_inc">3. malaria_inc：</h2>
<p><img src="https://github.com/akatuituji/Pic_blog/blob/master/20200922234001.png" alt="avatar" loading="lazy"><br>
We choose seabon package. We set x-axis: Year/Code, y-axis: Incidence. We will have 2 graphs.<br>
<img src="https://github.com/akatuituji/Pic_blog/blob/master/20200922233432.png" alt="avatar" loading="lazy"><br>
